ISLAMABAD, Oct 15 (APP):Prime Minister Imran Khan on Thursday condemned the attack on the convoy of Oil and Gas Development Company Limited (OGDCL) at Makran Coastal Highway, and sought report of the incident.
He commiserated with families of the security personnel martyred in the attack, lauded the services of the martyrs and prayed for the departed souls.
